  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of the ruler of your own medieval settlement, manage and develop it in real-time from a first-person perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect the Town Hall, which is the center of your settlement, and prevent the enemy from destroying it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/9ac6a3521654241cb28302125ae2df31.webp?t=1769266855\" width=600 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/526a3a2dc3d96dc003b567e98a83e80c.poster.avif?t=1769266855\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/526a3a2dc3d96dc003b567e98a83e80c.webm?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/526a3a2dc3d96dc003b567e98a83e80c.mp4?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Extract 5 types of resources.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Receive golden chests for developing your settlement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Produce arrows in the archery workshop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Look for berry bushes to provide food for your subjects.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/9d1253da3e86e7c54a024ddf9cab4a35.webp?t=1769266855\" width=600 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/0bcaf62360627a9a33ac25cbf94baa90.poster.avif?t=1769266855\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/0bcaf62360627a9a33ac25cbf94baa90.webm?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/0bcaf62360627a9a33ac25cbf94baa90.mp4?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Upgrade the Town Hall.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build 8 types of buildings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manage your settlement from the management panel.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/f5cef000fd088fd14f87e73990f74b33.webp?t=1769266855\" width=600 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/95e6d90a037d87f39a13b147b01804f5.poster.avif?t=1769266855\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/95e6d90a037d87f39a13b147b01804f5.webm?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/95e6d90a037d87f39a13b147b01804f5.mp4?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Search for resources on the map.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Search and collect or eat mushrooms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Destroy enemy 